This paper deals with selecting a certain number of data points from a database to satisfy users' expectations, which is a common problem in many applications, including hotel booking websites. This problem involves probability distribution and user satisfaction, which are relevant to the sub-categories of databases (cs.DB), artificial intelligence (cs.AI), data structures and algorithms (cs.DS), information retrieval (cs.IR), and machine learning (cs.LG). Therefore, these are the most likely sub-categories for this paper.
